title: Kapuzen
description:
With releases from Spinnin’ Records, Solotoko, Revealed, and more, Kapuzen will be making his headliner debut at Noite, the newest and hottest nightclub in San Jose. It will be a full night of bass-forward house music with supporting resident artists from the Dirty Not Sorry crew.

Want free entry? Text KAPUZEN at (415)237-0615 to receive your free guestlist before 11 pm.

M﻿usic Genre: House Music All Night

This will be a 21+ event.
